
### 创建一个规则：数字条件
POST http://localhost:8080/rule
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "规则2",
  "desc": "第一个规则",
  "condition": "c == 3"
}

### 使用规则
GET http://localhost:8080/rule/规则2?c=1

