### 创建一个规则：实际业务场景
POST http://localhost:8080/rule
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "政策业务规则",
  "desc": "订单中可下政策的限制规则",
  "condition": "department =~ ['1','2','3','4'] and workAge >= 0 and workAge <= 10  and customerLevel =~ ['39','40','41','42','43','44'] "
}

